lead_paragraph: Victoria Vivians had 22 points, Breanna Richardson added 21 and No. 5 Mississippi State cruised to a 106-30 victory over Northwestern State on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 5 Mississippi St Beats Northwestern St 106-30
